1 Preamble

1.1 Dependencies

library(Rarr)
library(EBImage)
library(jsonlite)
library(ImageArray)

1.2 Introduction

2 Setup

dir <- "extdata/mibitof/images/point8_image"
zarr <- system.file(file.path(dir, "0"), package = "ImageArray")
json <- system.file(file.path(dir, ".zattrs"), package = "ImageArray")

za <- read_zarr_array(zarr)
md <- fromJSON(json)
(ia <- ImageArray(za, md))
## class: ImageArray
## dim: 3 1024 1024 
## axes: c y x

3 Visualization

img <- data(aperm(ia))
plot(Image(img/255, dim(img), "Color"))
